{"tid":1559694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有國歌，當然要有國旗！香港需要新國旗！","createTime":"2019-09-11T02:25:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T04:19:19.000Z","uid":116054,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ec4017dfe051f81fa1d4b8d320fe5e5aae48fc17","tid":1559694,"uid":116054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:25:01.000Z","msg":"有國歌，當然要有國旗，建議連登搞個國旗設計比賽！<br />\n<br />\n原本用開的，或者有其他設計的，都全民投票再選出！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/11/102142_9e95aa500e2e12a2a78c6f07f26e2642.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F11%2F102142_9e95aa500e2e12a2a78c6f07f26e2642.jpg&h=4551dbcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n龍獅旗或稱龍獅香港旗，是香港自治運動或香港獨立運動的代表旗幟，於2011年5月由香港網民「金屬」設計。 該旗從香港殖民地時期的香港旗更改而來，去除了米字旗，僅使用原來面積比較小的香港盾徽，並且加上漢字「香港」，及配以象徵自由的貴族藍作為底色。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/11/102246_c064c2de58bd3f423c1158f2f1784803.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F11%2F102246_c064c2de58bd3f423c1158f2f1784803.jpg&h=d9a820be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都係香港人設計 有巴打將獅子轉埋做條龍 幾靚"},{"pid":"2469e40ac4d30d56dcf2434197913e38778a83e3","tid":1559694,"uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:25:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>914</strong></span></span> 天水圍親子遊行<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>915</strong></span></span> 民陣大遊行"},{"pid":"1b2ba5a7b3e4f15b07b2ef856f2ceee5c14db73c","tid":1559694,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:26:02.000Z","msg":"獅子型d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37390e7638bde2f0ba6946fde42c8101fb075d97","tid":1559694,"uid":20372,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:31:56.000Z","msg":"龍師更有意思 代表香港係中西文化交匯<img